text.tspan: Bipolar disorder prevalence, males vs. females, 2021

Estimated share of males versus females who have
bipolar disorder
, whether or not they are diagnosed, based on
representative surveys, medical data and statistical modelling.
Data source: IHME, Global Burden of Disease (2024)

Note: To allow for comparisons between countries and over time, this metric is
age-standardized
.
